{"tid":2212675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"常理判決：以政治人物作為襲擊目標，是加刑因素；另一個異類：老藍絲當面行刺長毛，官：熱愛社會，減至免於監禁","createTime":"2020-09-22T04:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T07:16:17.000Z","uid":230104,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1919e290ca0ef79882ab28f6103720188c0cb78","tid":2212675,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰去年8月在佐敦與友人午膳期間，遭兩名蒙面南亞裔男子持棒球棍及牛肉刀闖入餐廳施襲，友人用手擋棍受傷。售貨員及後認罪，承認招攬15歲少年夥同犯案，指使對方駕駛失車接載兇徒，少年則經審訊後被裁定串謀蓄意傷人等罪成。區域法院法官陳仲衡今判刑時形容襲擊邪惡，其中售貨員招攬未成年人士犯案，令人髮指，且以政治人物為目標，屬加刑因素；為免他人中仿效，重判售貨員入獄46個月，少年則入住教導所，另兩人須停牌18個月。"},{"pid":"9a5973b776557bd001d4ccca2ab6596f26763db0","tid":2212675,"uid":84408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"講個笑話你知：香港法治"},{"pid":"208019fd72ad03ad9f3b636441a1dff074550591","tid":2212675,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"刺殺政治人物後竟被稱讚熱愛社會，係咪變相鼓勵更多藍絲效法？"},{"pid":"70de1b1e8e55ff4a1c2330fc61c34ab74cd24055","tid":2212675,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fb4e9b89a01e7004acfe34799b77eae122b255","tid":2212675,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"真係要搬離非主流法官審核地區"},{"pid":"76e1f8f48a321096fb7a5dcdfff24cb138f20d40","tid":2212675,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"個官係時候被升職"},{"pid":"ba38cf164aa1645b9ded7c0091ad75e3b296e4a1","tid":2212675,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xqo5voP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F